title: [Necropolis, Narthex]
description: A huge pile of bones dominates the center of the room.  Femurs, phalanges, tibias, skulls, and other various bones lay jumbled in a pile nearly the height of a giantman.  Deep teeth marks mar each bone, and most of the longer ones have been broken in half.
paths: Obvious exits: north, northeast, east, southeast, south, southwest, west, northwest
